        "content": "<p>I was surprised to find that <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_docs/tactics.html#interval_cases\">tactic#interval_cases</a> struggles on intervals with more than one or two items, for instance:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">tactic.interval_cases</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">set_option</span> <span class=\"n\">profiler</span> <span class=\"n\">true</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">example</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">i</span> <span class=\"bp\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"mi\">5</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">true</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span> <span class=\"n\">interval_cases</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span> <span class=\"n\">trivial</span>  <span class=\"c1\">-- 985ms</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">example</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">i</span> <span class=\"bp\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"mi\">6</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">true</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span> <span class=\"n\">interval_cases</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span> <span class=\"n\">trivial</span>  <span class=\"c1\">-- 1.88s</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">example</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">i</span> <span class=\"bp\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"mi\">7</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">true</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span> <span class=\"n\">interval_cases</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span> <span class=\"n\">trivial</span>  <span class=\"c1\">-- 3.35s</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">example</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">i</span> <span class=\"bp\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"mi\">8</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">true</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span> <span class=\"n\">interval_cases</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span> <span class=\"n\">trivial</span>  <span class=\"c1\">-- 6.2s</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>The runtime appears to be exponential in the length of the interval!</p>\n<p>Does this look like a deep refl causing the issue?</p>",
